steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Team" without submenu
Then I should see Team screen display
When I invite new email "jitera" with timestamp
Then I should see the warning popup with message "User invitation sent successfully"
Then I should see row index "1" has Name "empty" - email timestamp - status "pending invitation"
Then I should see inbox of email "timestamp" has "1" emails
When I resend invitation for user row "1"
Then I should see the warning popup with message "User invitation resent successfully"
